@sonic: in order to keep with the idea that it plays off the tutorial game I would strongly suggest we stay with 'Bob' and a defibrillator, if for no other reason than to help judging.  If it helps, you could always employ casting [i:2xu9sfb2]defibrillate[/i:2xu9sfb2] on Sir Robert to revive him, or you could use a defibrilaticus to revive a roman.
